---
const title = "DOULAS by the BAY | SF Bay Area Doula Support Services";
const description = "Professional birth and postpartum doula services in the San Francisco Bay Area. Expert support for pregnancy, childbirth, and newborn care since 2009.";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description}>
  <meta name="keywords" content="doula, birth support, postpartum care, San Francisco Bay Area, pregnancy support">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-container">
        <h1 class="logo">DOULAS by the BAY</h1>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
          <a href="/courses-cart">Courses</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Are you worried about navigating pregnancy, birth, and the initial weeks with your newborn?</h1>
        <p>Expecting families often navigate a sea of emotions, with anticipation and concerns about their journey ahead.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555252333-9f8e92e65df9?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Pregnant woman with support">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
      <h2>Our Doula Services</h2>
      <p>We are a team of Birth, Postpartum Doulas and Newborn Care Specialists who are dedicated to supporting families before, during and immediately after childbirth.</p>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?w=400&h=300&fit=crop" alt="Birth Support">
          <h3>Birth Support</h3>
          <p>Professional guidance through labor and delivery with compassionate care.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578662996442-48f60103fc96?w=400&h=300&fit=crop" alt="Postpartum Support">
          <h3>Postpartum Support</h3>
          <p>Expert care and assistance during your recovery and early parenting journey.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559252333-1c12d6012e9a?w=400&h=300&fit=crop" alt="Newborn Care">
          <h3>Newborn Care</h3>
          <p>Specialized care for your newborn with certified specialists.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-preview">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Proudly Serving the San Francisco Bay Area Since 2009</h2>
        <p>What makes Doulas by the Bay unique is our large, diverse team that has worked with thousands of parents and babies. Our team of professionals is trained and certified, fully vetted, CPR certified.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="learn-more">Learn More About Us</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="resources">
      <h2>Educational Videos & Resources</h2>
      <div class="resource-grid">
        <article class="resource-item">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160399-112ba8d25d1f?w=400&h=250&fit=crop" alt="Modern Childbirth">
          <h3>The Vital Role of Doulas in Modern Childbirth</h3>
          <p>Childbirth is a deeply personal and transformative journey, and having the right support along the way can bring comfort, confidence, and peace.</p>
          <span class="date">Apr 29, 2025</span>
        </article>
        <article class="resource-item">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=400&h=250&fit=crop" alt="Postpartum Depression">
          <h3>Postpartum Depression PPD: A Comprehensive Guide</h3>
          <p>Postpartum depression (PPD) is a significant concern for many new parents. This guide aims to provide comprehensive understanding of PPD.</p>
          <span class="date">Apr 16, 2025</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta">
      <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
      <p>We're here to help</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get In Touch</a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3>DOULAS by the BAY</h3>
        <p>Supporting families in the San Francisco Bay Area since 2009.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Services</h4>
        <a href="#">Birth Support</a>
        <a href="#">Postpartum Support</a>
        <a href="#">Newborn Care</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h4>Resources</h4>
        <a href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a href="#">Reviews</a>
        <a href="#">Service Area</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 4rem auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #2c5aa0;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background: #1e3f73;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .services {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .services h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .services > p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    .service-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .service-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .service-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0.5rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .service-card p {
      padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    .about-preview {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .about-preview h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .about-preview p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    .learn-more {
      color: #2c5aa0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 2px solid #2c5aa0;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .learn-more:hover {
      background: #2c5aa0;
      color: white;
    }

    .resources {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .resources h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .resource-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .resource-item {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .resource-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .resource-item h3 {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0.5rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .resource-item p {
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    .date {
      display: block;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .contact-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: #2c5aa0;
      color: white;
    }

    .contact-cta h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-cta p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-cta .cta-button {
      background: white;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .contact-cta .cta-button:hover {
      background: #f0f0f0;
    }

    footer {
      background: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
    }

    .footer-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-section h3,
    .footer-section h4 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2c5aa0;
    }

    .footer-section a {
      display: block;
      color: #ccc;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .footer-section a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .service-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .resource-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>